[h2]Clear Data[/h2]

[b]Options Menu > Extension Options > Station Ware History > Clear Data[/b]: with data collection disabled, tick [b]Confirm Clearing Collected Data[/b] and click [b]Clear Data[/b] to permanently delete all recorded history for every station.

